Fourth Department,

September, 1946.

(September 18, 1946.) In the Matter of Rochester Co-operative Milk Producers Bargaining Agency, Inc., et al., Petitioners, against C. Chester Du Mond, as Commissioner of Agriculture and Markets of the State of New York, et al., Respondents.

Transferred to the Appellate Division of the Supreme Court, Third Department, for hearing and determination. Present — Taylor, P. J., Dowling, Harris, McCurn and Larkin, JJ.
